    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Log-frame houses, common in Northern Russia, primarily rural, but found in urban areas until the 17th and 18th centuries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
